I increased the hydration to 80%. He didn't soak his seeds which
I think this will cause his dough to dry out. His effective
hydration by my calculations was 47% using the seed hydration
numbers from
https://www.thefreshloaf.com/node/61245/soaker-ingredient-hydration-percents-some-data

I added 0.2% yeast because my starter is slow to rise.

